                            <head><hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi></head>
                            <p>—At the morning meeting of the Foreign Ministers (<hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, page 145) it was agreed that they would meet at 3:45
                                p.m. The <hi rend="italic">Rapporteur’s</hi> report (<hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, page 158) indicates that the meeting
                                was actually held, but no minutes therefor have been found.</p>
